entries.title_d: The Dantooine station wants you to commit a few acts of piracy in order to get them some more supplies. Your first task is to inspect a freighter called the Shifty Prince. It should be carrying some phasotron radium that the station is in need of.
entries.title: Naboo System: Inspect the Shifty Prince
entries.split_quest_alert: The Phasotron Radium is now safely in your possession. Travel to Corellia and capture the Bez'ox Mentzz.
entries.quest_location_d: The Shifty Prince is currently located inside of the Naboo system.
entries.quest_inspect_d: Inspect the freighter and make sure that it has the phasotron radium on it.
entries.quest_dock_d: Dock with the freighter and transfer the cargo onto your ship.
